Date: Thu, 1 Oct 1998 08:33:58 GMT -0600 CST
From: "Dennis Perrotta" <Dennis.Perrotta@tdh.state.tx.us>

The ATSDR ToxProfile on TCE reports a 1984 article reporting SJS in
five people occupationally exposed to TCE for 2-5 weeks at levels
from 19-164ppm. (Contact Dermatitis Vol 10, pp270-276.)
